snippet: Tina Charles and the Liberty ended a disappointing season with a victory, just barely missing the W.N.B.A. playoffs for the second straight season.
abstract: New York Liberty defeats Indiana Fever, 73-61, to close out 2014 regular season; Liberty fails to make playoffs for second straight season.
